{
  "stem": "13874.5",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And if finally, the Nazis were ready to release him, they said, now, you will be released under one condition-- that you do not talk about it.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "As soon as you talk about it, you come right back here, and you won't get out.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So it was completely hushed up that we are Germans.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And as I said before, the impression created was the impression they wanted to create, and that was a screen with which they could prepare for the war without too much interference from the ally.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You had a German Bund.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You had, in the United States, you had similar organizations all over the world, who tacitly approved of what Germany was doing, who influenced-- influenced the government in the war.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "One of the greatest German supporters was Joseph P.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Kennedy.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "As this is known.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And he wasn't the only one.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But Hitler wanted to create that impression that everything else within Germany is fine, and it's only the Jews, the vagrants, homosexuals-- there's others-- and to-- who keeps it-- to keeps the streets clean.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Nobody really knew the-- it was-- the extent of the Jews in the concentration camp wasn't known.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But less known, much less known, was the extent to really the way the Germans were treated there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I said, Dachau was for-- for two years without a single Jew-- just as an example.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And when the war broke out, nobody cared anymore what went out, or that nothing went out anyway.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Hitler had achieved what he wanted to achieve.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And he used the Jews.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "He used homosexuals, the gypsies, whatever it is, as a cover.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "We were-- and as such, we were very-- he was very successful.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And that shouldn't be overlook.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
